<HEADLINE>
Report: Explosion near Beersheva bus station
</HEADLINE>

<TEXT>
	   BEERSHEVA, Israel (AP) _ An explosion went off near the bus
station in the southern town of Beersheva Monday injuring some 10
people lightly, Army Radio reported.
	   An eyewitness told Israel Radio that he saw a young man throw
two hand grenades in quick succession. No further details were
immediately available.
