materials in the Paula Jones case could begin yet another round of
embarrassing revelations about President Bill Clinton's sex life.
US-CLINTON-JONES. Expected by 0700 GMT. Lead expected with release
of documents at 1000 GMT. By James Jefferson. AP Photo NY107.
	   CAIRO, Egypt _ Rescue teams end their search for survivors of a
train that jumped its tracks and crashed into a crowded platform in
northern Egypt, killing about 50 people. EGYPT-TRAIN CRASH. Has
moved; developments will be expedited. By Tarek El-Tablawy. AP
Photo LON101.
	   TAIPEI, Taiwan _ Taiwan's chief negotiator with China returns
home Monday after a five-day visit to the mainland as the island
assesses the impact of his path-breaking visit, which included a
meeting with President Jiang Zemin. TAIWAN-CHINA. Expected by 0700
GMT. By Annie Huang.
	   ISLAMABAD, Pakistan _ The vaguely worded statement that emerged
from talks between India and Pakistan has done little to ease
global worries about the development of nuclear weapons by the
historic enemies. ANALYSIS-PAKISTAN-INDIA. Has moved. By Kathy
Gannon.
