ARGENTINA &QL; 
 &UR; Results:

<TEXT>
	   Huracan 2, Platense 1 (Friday)
	   Belgrano Cordoba 3, Racing 2 (Saturday)
	   Boca Juniors 2, Velez Sarsfield 0
	   Gimnasia Jujuy 2, River Plate 2
	   Newell's Old Boys 0, Argentinos Juniors 0
	   Union 3, San Lorenzo 6
	   Lanus 1, Talleres Cordoba 4
	   Independiente 1, Rosario Central 1
	   Gimnasia La Plata 4, Colon 2
	   Ferro Carril Oeste vs.Estudiantes de La Plata (Monday)
	   Standings: Boca 27 points; Gimnasia La Plata 21; Lanus and
