on Monday for a brief visit after taking part in the weekend
Ibero-American summit in Portugal. APTN has a wrap. (FIRST RUN 0300
EUROPE EARLY)
----
TEXAS: FLOODING - Coverage of the appalling weather conditions in
Texas, where at least 14 people have been killed since Saturday.
(FIRST RUN AFTER 0300)
----
