embassy in the capital of Chile, a soundbite from the daughter of
one of Pinochet's victims, voxpops from Chileans supporting the
arrest of the former dictator, reaction from the Mothers of the
Plaza de Mayo in Argentina and coverage of an anti-Pinochet protest
outside the London clinic where he is undergoing medical treatment.
(WRAP FIRST RUN 0300 EUROPE)
----
